# Figma to Tailwind Theme Mapping

When the user shares Figma data (via link selection or MCP tool), always map Figma values to the project's theme variables defined in `src/styles.css`.

## Color Mapping

| Figma Hex | Tailwind Class | CSS Variable |
|-----------|----------------|--------------|
| `#321000` | `brand-dark` | `--color-brand-dark` |
| `#C9B08D` / `#c9b08d` | `brand-tan` | `--color-brand-tan` |
| `#9E4F00` / `#9e4f00` | `brand-orange` | `--color-brand-orange` |
| `#FAF3E7` / `#faf3e7` | `brand-cream` | `--color-brand-cream` |
| `#1C1D1B` / `#1c1d1b` | `brand-charcoal` | `--color-brand-charcoal` |
| `#E9E9E9` / `#e9e9e9` | `brand-gray` | `--color-brand-gray` |

