## Font Weight Mapping

| Figma Weight | Tailwind Class |
|--------------|----------------|
| `300` / Light | `font-light` |
| `400` / Regular | `font-normal` |
| `500` / Medium | `font-medium` |
| `600` / SemiBold | `font-semibold` |
| `700` / Bold | `font-bold` |

## Example

```tsx
// ❌ BAD - Using raw Figma values
<h1 style={{ fontFamily: 'Sora', fontSize: '80px', color: '#321000' }}>

// ✅ GOOD - Using theme variables
<h1 className="font-sora text-h1 text-brand-dark font-bold">
```

Always prefer Tailwind classes over inline styles or arbitrary values.
